        <abstract> 
<p>Thanks for <hi rend="italic">Botanische Zeitung</hi> notice of CD’s paper ["On the character and hybrid-like nature of the offspring from the illegitimate unions of dimorphic and trimorphic plants", <hi rend="italic">J. Linn. Soc. Lond. (Bot.)</hi> 10 (1869): 393–437]. FH writes clearest style of all German authors.</p> 
            <p>Asks that August Weismann be told about papers by Wallace and Bates.</p>
        </abstract>
